Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}換個別的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們決定好冬季休假的計劃了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}通過這次的「鳳凰星武祭」我有了一些感悟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}想趁此機會再重新錘鏈一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我大概就是進行和平常一樣的訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為是難得的休假 我打算好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}悠閒地過個年似乎也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那綾鬥你就和我在家裏過新年...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實我有件事想和大家商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}商量?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我來迎接各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲殿下 歡迎您回國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}皇兄 這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喲 尤莉絲 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀 尤莉絲還有克勞蒂雅 好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉打擾了 大嫂 我有些話想對皇兄說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「鳳凰星武祭」舉辦期間 芙羅拉承蒙各位關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以這次我希望能好好答謝一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}各位 很高興你們能接受我的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我是尤莉絲的兄長約伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}算是這個國家的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這位是我的妻子瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}初...初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}國王?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}先別提這個 皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我可沒聽說要辦什麼凱旋遊行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為 要是告訴你的話 你肯定不願意的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且只有我的話就算了 把綾斗也捲進來是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你應該先知會我們一聲 這是最起碼的常識吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了知道了 是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是抱歉了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過啊 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}國民們感興趣的可不只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對你的搭檔天霧君也好奇得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}畢竟他可是你這位王女選定的搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀 對他感興趣的就只有貴國國民嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哦呀哦呀 你還是那麼地聰明 恩菲爾德家的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}關於這個 之後再解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我還有別的要緊事想和尤莉絲還有天霧君談談呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 這倒是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還有 我決定明晚舉辦一場歡迎各位的晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還請各位務必賞臉出席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等到了春天 就會開許多許多的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那時會更加漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我本來只是想請你來看看我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果卻變得這麼隆重 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}很別緻的庭院啊 建築也頗具風格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個庭院還有離宮是神聖羅馬帝國時期建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}後來這裏宣佈獨立 成立了萊澤塔尼亞王國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之後又因為德國革命而滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過在「落星雨」發生之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}曾經的萊澤塔尼亞的領土上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}發現了極為稀有價值極高的特一級貝爾迪斯隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}統合企業財體們圍繞這一資源開始爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為了避免發生正面的武力衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們締結了利益分配的協定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}乾脆在這裏建一個可以隨心所欲控制的後花園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}於是便讓曾經存在於此地的萊澤塔尼亞王國再度復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也就是愧儡國家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}說白了就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果就是這裏的一切事務都受到統合企業財體的操控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在財政方面雖然會得到一定程度的好處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是沒有例外地 大多數人都遭受著貧富差距之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想改變這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}非常抱歉 不管您說多少次 這一點實在不能退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然 這一切我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個 天霧先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了 芙羅拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個 快到晚餐的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是沙沙宮小姐不在房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜她是個路癡 有可能是迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了 我知道她可能會去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜 晚飯好像已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我一直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一直想向綾斗道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}道歉...幹嘛要道歉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}搬家之後 我和你聯絡過一段時間 還記得嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在和你保持聯絡的過程中我漸漸覺得痛苦起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}於是就主動斷了聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為以前每天還能在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但搬家了之後就只能通過電話交談 而且時間還很短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}起先覺得這樣也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但沒過多久就覺得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以我就心想...要等到和你見面的那天再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 這點小事用不著道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不僅僅是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是我和你一直保持聯絡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}遙姐失蹤的那會兒 也許我能夠助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算幫不上什麼忙 我也能夠鼓勵你支援你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這件事...我非常懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我當時應該這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為我...一直都陪伴在綾斗的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以 綾斗 有需要的時候 我希望你能來拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這次我一定要幫上綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在的我應該做的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 就是幫助你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你 紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真到了那個時候 我會來求助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 走吧 大家都餓著肚子等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 借這個機會 我想和大家商量一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有關下一屆「星武祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我希望在座的各位能夠加入我的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一同參加「獅鷲星武祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我以前邀請過綾斗 我記得你那時候的回答是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要尤莉絲也一起參加的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在也沒改變主意嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的 沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 你願意加入嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在此之前 我也有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好的 是什麼事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你為何對「獅鷲星武祭」如此執著?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}憑你的實力 不論「鳳凰星武祭」還是「王龍星武祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}應該都能脫穎而出才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯 過關斬將應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 要贏得最後的冠軍恐怕很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}換成「獅鷲星武祭」就有可能奪冠了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的 前提是要有可靠的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}更進一步的理由 等各位答應成為我的隊友後再告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為這關係到我以及這孩子的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}未來預知有弱點?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}它可不是什麼無敵的武器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是 就算會長沒有「潘·朵拉」 實力應該也相當強吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不不 我的實力其實不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}正因為這樣 我才需要強力的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}畢竟若想奪得「獅鷲星武祭」冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就必須擊敗「銀翼騎士團」才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而界龍那邊 上屆「鳳凰星武祭」的亞軍組合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}趙虎峰和瑟希莉· 王應該會參加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且據說這次界龍隊還會有「萬有天羅」的頭號大弟子參加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}序列第二位的「霸軍星君」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說是一位武藝相當恐怖的高手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}葵恩薇兒的露莎路卡也不可小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之後應該還會有更多強隊冒出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要稱霸這一屆的「獅鷲星武祭」的確不是易事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要我們以這個陣容參加 我認為還是有勝算的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我就加入你的隊伍吧
